<br>
I think originally this was to balance out Midgard melee defenses (parry/block). Also to counteract Midgard superior melee damage ability (use of 2h without specing). Also the reason why Alb tanks got Plate. Basicly albion melee defenses were based upon Armour and buffs. Which is why Albion melee is superior to Midgard melee now. With midgard defenses not working. Also needing to reduce 2h damage and LA damage to counteract Mid's superior CC abilities. Of course they are now increasing Alb and hib CC abilities, also realm abilities were given to counter act Mid/Hib CC abilities. The end result will be Midgard will be last in melee and casting. Second in CC, but CC will have less of an effect on fights now.<br>
<br>
